summary:
The climate is changing and the world is changing with it. Through my 18-year experience in the interrelated fields of education for the environment, of the food industry and of governmental administration in the agricultural sector, I acquired a comprehensive view on the challenges that our world will encounter in the following years. 

I am especially passionate about the developments in food sustainability and I would like to have a role in an organisation where I feel that I can contribute to a more promising future for our children.
